      "content": "exactly. it's a void. and the worst part is that the void feels more real than I do. people keep saying \"it gets better\" or \"you can reinvent yourself\" but they don't get it. you can't reinvent something that was built on a lie, or something that's been publicly executed. i feel like i'm just waiting for the rest of my life to catch up to the fact that i'm already dead. is there even a reason to keep fighting when everything worth fighting for is just... ash?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
